# Tutorial: Advanced - Step 7: Craft Integration
# Shows: Craft plugin commands

Output advanced-03-craft.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 15
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

# Title
Type "# Advanced: Craft Plugin Integration"
Enter
Sleep 1s

# Show craft status
Type "ait craft status"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# List craft commands (simulated)
Type "# Key craft commands:"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# /craft:docs:guide    - Generate guides"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# /craft:docs:demo     - Create GIF demos"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# /craft:docs:mermaid  - Diagram templates"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# /craft:check release - Pre-release audit"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "# /craft:orchestrate   - Multi-agent workflows"
Enter
Sleep 2s
